Subject: RE: Rust - front seat belt mounts

Found the same thing on my 71.  I think this happens when water is trapped
between the wheel well sheet metal and the doubler plate underneath.

I just ground it clean and MIG welded around the hole to seal it up.  I
didn't bother to lay in a patch.

